The Chronicle Pictures by Nkosizile Ndlovu Police are looking for the hooligans who went on the rampage during the Castle Challenge Cup match pitting Highlanders and FC Platinum at Barbourfields Stadium on Saturday. Chronicle captured the acts of violence and we are appealing to members of the public to help identify the hooligans so that they may face the full wrath of the law. CLICK ON GALLERY BELOW TO VIEW IMAGES 